data.enText: to formally or officially tell sb about sth

data.chText: 将发信通知竞赛的优胜者。
data.enText: Competition winners will be notified by post.

data.chText: 必须向警方报告游行示威的日期。
data.enText: The police must be notified of the date of the demonstration.

data.chText: 游行示威的日期必须报告警方。
data.enText: The date of the demonstration must be notified to the police.

simple_means.memory_skill: not 知道 + ify 使… → 使…知道 → 通知

ex.chText: 时间如有变更，我们将尽快通知你们。
ex.enText: We will inform you of any change of time as soon as possible.

ex.chText: 我们很高兴地通知你，你被聘用了。
ex.enText: We are glad to inform you that you have been hired.

ex.chText: 老师会把该学生取得的任何进步都告诉其家长。
ex.enText: The teacher will inform the parents of any progress the pupil has made.

synonyms.bx: 指将事情或信息正式地告知某人。

ex.enText: You need to acquaint me with the truth.

ex.chText: 她得告诉新老板公司近来的动态。
ex.enText: She has to acquaint her new boss with recent happenings in the company.

ex.chText: 她想知道你有哪些长处以及不足。
ex.enText: She wants to acquaint herself with your strengths and weaknesses.

synonyms.bx: 指将某事告知某人，通常用于 acquaint sb with sth 结构。

ex.chText: 如果地址有变，请尽快通知我。
ex.enText: Please notify/inform me of any change of address as soon as possible.

ex.chText: 他们接到通知，说会议被取消了。
ex.enText: They were notified/informed that the meeting was canceled.

synonyms.bx: 指正式地或由官方通知某人某事，常可与 inform 换用。

example: I advised him that the rent was due

value.def: If you notify someone of something, you officially inform them about it.

example.ex: The skipper notified the coastguard of the tragedy...
example.tran: 船长向海岸警卫队报告了这起灾难。

example.ex: Earlier this year they were notified that their homes were to be cleared away...
example.tran: 今年早些时候他们接到通知说他们的房屋要拆迁。

example.ex: She confirmed that she would notify the police and the hospital.
example.tran: 她确认说她会通知警方和医院。

rootsaffixes.indicate: = to know, mark 知道；标记
rootsaffixes.title: not

an 加强 + not 知道；标记 + ation 行为，过程，状态，结果 → 注解
de 加强 + not 知道；标记 + e → 做标记 → 指示
not 知道；标记 + able …的 → 加了标记的 → 值得注意的
not 知道；标记 + ice 表行为 → 使知道；做标记引起注意 → 注意；通知
not 知道；标记 + ify 使… → 使…知道 → 通知
not 知道；标记 + ion 表名词 → 为让人知道而表达的自己的见解和观点 → 见解；观念
not 知道；标记 + or 表人 + ious 多…的 →〔因做坏事〕让很多人知道 → 恶名昭彰的
